    60    // We pass skip_cluster_check=true to factoryForGrpcService in order to avoid throwing
    61    // exceptions in worker threads. Call sites of this getOrCreateLogger must check the cluster
    62    // availability via ClusterManager::checkActiveStaticCluster beforehand, and throw exceptions in
